    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《恶魔秘境》是一款玩法独特的Roguelike卡牌游戏，这是一款需要联网的Roguelike卡牌游戏，我们要赶在强大的恶魔到来之前，在秘境中探索各类事件，努力丰富牌组、强化实力！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索阶段</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恶魔的秘境分为3层，每一层中我们有20天的时间探索地图并提升实力，20天后BOSS即将降临。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一天我们都可以探索一个自身周围的未知区域，每隔五天将有一个恶魔的爪牙来袭！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093320/extras/59666ce7c0574ed58feaecca16d15cff.poster.avif?t=1747710123\" width=618 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093320/extras/59666ce7c0574ed58feaecca16d15cff.webm?t=1747710123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093320/extras/59666ce7c0574ed58feaecca16d15cff.mp4?t=1747710123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>对战阶段</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗中，每回合都可以选择献祭一张卡牌来提升法力上限。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用手牌和技能都要消耗法力。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤出的生物会在回合结束时自动攻击正前方的敌方生物。正前方如果没有生物就会攻击对手。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093320/extras/68f9d8f865ab6e90966a667113ea9e0a.poster.avif?t=1747710123\" width=618 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093320/extras/68f9d8f865ab6e90966a667113ea9e0a.webm?t=1747710123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093320/extras/68f9d8f865ab6e90966a667113ea9e0a.mp4?t=1747710123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>献祭什么卡牌，法力如何利用，生物如何站位……都需要作出选择。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]独特的战斗系统</p></strong></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原创的战斗机制，和其他卡牌游戏的差异较大，而且作战双方都在使用卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]Roguelike元素</p></strong></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机生成的秘境世界，每一次冒险都是一次全新的探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]牌组构筑玩法</p></strong></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险过程中将会逐步加强初始套牌，每一次冒险都会形成不一样的打法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]丰富的内容</p></strong></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当前版本包含340多张卡牌，110多种道具，80多种怪物，以及12个截然不同的英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]高难度的挑战</p></strong></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有13重难度可以挑战，高难度下每一次选择都需要深思熟虑</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恶魔即将降临，勇士们，是时候拿起你的武器了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >联系我们</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群:591891578 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord:HZ9G2wG</p>",
